parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door lock actuator can cause the doors to lock and unlock unexpectedly, potentially trapping occupants inside the vehicle or leaving them vulnerable to theft. This can also lead to accidents or injuries if the doors open or close suddenly while driving.
symptoms: The doors lock and unlock unexpectedly
the doors do not stay locked or unlocked
the doors make a loud noise when locking or unlocking
the doors lock or unlock while driving
the doors do not respond to the key fob or door controls.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause the vehicle to stall or fail to start, leading to accidents or injuries, especially if the vehicle loses power while driving.
symptoms: The vehicle fails to start
the vehicle stalls while driving
the dashboard lights flicker or illuminate
the vehicle makes a low whirring noise when trying to start.
